{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Num|28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","chapter":28,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":1,"text":"The Lord spoke to Moses,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":2,"text":"“Command the Israelites and say to them: Be sure to present to me at its appointed time my offering and my food as my food offering, a pleasing aroma to me.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":3,"text":"And say to them: This is the food offering you are to present to the Lord:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":4,"text":"Offer one lamb in the morning and the other lamb at twilight,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":5,"text":"along with two quarts of fine flour for a grain offering mixed with a quart of olive oil from crushed olives.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":6,"text":"It is a regular burnt offering established at Mount Sinai for a pleasing aroma, a food offering to the Lord.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":7,"text":"The drink offering is to be a quart with each lamb. Pour out the offering of beer to the Lord in the sanctuary area.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":8,"text":"Offer the second lamb at twilight, along with the same kind of grain offering and drink offering as in the morning. It is a food offering, a pleasing aroma to the Lord.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":9,"text":"“On the Sabbath day present two unblemished year-old male lambs, four quarts of fine flour mixed with oil as a grain offering, and its drink offering.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":10,"text":"It is the burnt offering for every Sabbath, in addition to the regular burnt offering and its drink offering.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":11,"text":"“At the beginning of each of your months present a burnt offering to the Lord: two young bulls, one ram, seven male lambs a year old —all unblemished —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":12,"text":"with six quarts of fine flour mixed with oil as a grain offering for each bull, four quarts of fine flour mixed with oil as a grain offering for the ram,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":13,"text":"and two quarts of fine flour mixed with oil as a grain offering for each lamb. It is a burnt offering, a pleasing aroma, a food offering to the Lord.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":14,"text":"Their drink offerings are to be two quarts of wine with each bull, one and a third quarts with the ram, and one quart with each male lamb. This is the monthly burnt offering for all the months of the year.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":15,"text":"And one male goat is to be offered as a sin offering to the Lord, in addition to the regular burnt offering with its drink offering.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":16,"text":"“The Passover to the Lord comes in the first month, on the fourteenth day of the month.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":17,"text":"On the fifteenth day of this month there will be a festival; unleavened bread is to be eaten for seven days.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":18,"text":"On the first day there is to be a sacred assembly; you are not to do any daily work.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":19,"text":"Present a food offering, a burnt offering to the Lord: two young bulls, one ram, and seven male lambs a year old. Your animals are to be unblemished.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":20,"text":"The grain offering with them is to be of fine flour mixed with oil; offer six quarts with each bull and four quarts with the ram.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":21,"text":"Offer two quarts with each of the seven lambs","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":22,"text":"and one male goat for a sin offering to make atonement for yourselves.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":23,"text":"Offer these with the morning burnt offering that is part of the regular burnt offering.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":24,"text":"You are to offer the same food each day for seven days as a food offering, a pleasing aroma to the Lord. It is to be offered with its drink offering and the regular burnt offering.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":25,"text":"On the seventh day you are to hold a sacred assembly; you are not to do any daily work.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":26,"text":"“On the day of firstfruits, you are to hold a sacred assembly when you present an offering of new grain to the Lord at your Festival of Weeks; you are not to do any daily work.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":27,"text":"Present a burnt offering as a pleasing aroma to the Lord: two young bulls, one ram, and seven male lambs a year old,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":28,"text":"with their grain offering of fine flour mixed with oil, six quarts with each bull, four quarts with the ram,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":29,"text":"and two quarts with each of the seven lambs,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:30","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":30,"text":"and one male goat to make atonement for yourselves.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:31","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","bookOrder":3,"chapter":28,"verse":31,"text":"Offer them with their drink offerings in addition to the regular burnt offering and its grain offering. Your animals are to be unblemished.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Num","chapter":28,"paragraphStarts":[1,4,9,11,16,26],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Prescribed Offerings"},{"beforeVerse":4,"text":"Daily Offerings"},{"beforeVerse":9,"text":"Sabbath Offerings"},{"beforeVerse":11,"text":"Monthly Offerings"},{"beforeVerse":16,"text":"Offerings for Passover"},{"beforeVerse":26,"text":"Offerings for the Festival of Weeks"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" spoke to Moses, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Command the Israelites and say to them: Be sure to present to me at its appointed time my offering and my foo