ing aroma, a food offering to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit one-tenth (of an ephah), also in vv. 21,29"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Their drink offerings are to be two quarts "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit a half hin"},{"kind":"text","text":" of wine with each bull, one and a third quarts "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Lit bull, a third hin"},{"kind":"text","text":" with the ram, and one quart "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":5,"text":"Lit a fourth hin"},{"kind":"text","text":" with each male lamb. This is the monthly burnt offering for all the months of the year. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Lit a half hin"},{"marker":4,"text":"Lit bull, a third hin"},{"marker":5,"text":"Lit a fourth hin"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And one male goat is to be offered as a sin offering to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", in addition to the regular burnt offering with its drink offering."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“The Passover "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 12:18","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:5","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 45:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":45,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" comes in the first month, on the fourteenth day of the month. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 12:18","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":18},{"label":"Lv 23:5","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":5},{"label":"Ezk 45:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":45,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On the fifteenth day of this month there will be a festival; unleavened bread is to be eaten for seven days. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On the first day there is to be a sacred assembly; you are not to do any daily work. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 12:16","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:3","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:7","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:28","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":28,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 29:7","book":"Num","chapter":29,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 12:16","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":16},{"label":"Lv 23:3","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":3},{"label":"Lv 23:7","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":7},{"label":"Lv 23:28","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":28},{"label":"Nm 29:7","book":"Num","chapter":29,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Present a food offering, a burnt offering to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":": two young bulls, one ram, and seven male lambs a year old. Your animals are to be unblemished. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 22:20","book":"Lev","chapter":22,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 29:8","book":"Num","chapter":29,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 29:13","book":"Num","chapter":29,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 15:21","book":"Deu","chapter":15,"verse":21,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 17:1","book":"Deu","chapter":17,"verse":1,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 22:20","book":"Lev","chapter":22,"verse":20},{"label":"Nm 29:8","book":"Num","chapter":29,"verse":8},{"label":"Nm 29:13","book":"Num","chapter":29,"verse":13},{"label":"Dt 15:21","book":"Deu","chapter":15,"verse":21},{"label":"Dt 17:1","book":"Deu","chapter":17,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The grain offering with them is to be of fine flour mixed with oil; offer six quarts with each bull and four quarts with the ram. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Offer two quarts with each of the seven lambs "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and one male goat for a sin offering to make atonement for yourselves. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Offer these with the morning burnt offering that is part of the regular burnt offering. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You are to offer the same food each day for seven days as a food offering, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 12:16","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 13:6","book":"Exo","chapter":13,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:8","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" a pleasing aroma to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". It is to be offered with its drink offering and the regular burnt offering. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 12:16","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":16},{"label":"Ex 13:6","book":"Exo","chapter":13,"verse":6},{"label":"Lv 23:8","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On the seventh day you are to hold a sacred assembly; you are not to do any daily work."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“On the day of firstfruits, you are to hold a sacred assembly when you present an offering of new grain to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" at your Festival of Weeks; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 23:16","book":"Exo","chapter":23,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 34:22","book":"Exo","chapter":34,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:10","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:15","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":15,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 16:9","book":"Deu","chapter":16,"verse":9,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:1","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":1,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" you are not to do any daily work. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 23:16","book":"Exo","chapter":23,"verse":16},{"label":"Ex 34:22","book":"Exo","chapter":34,"verse":22},{"label":"Lv 23:10","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":10},{"label":"Lv 23:15","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":15},{"label":"Dt 16:9","book":"Deu","chapter":16,"verse":9},{"label":"Ac 2:1","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Present a burnt offering as a pleasing aroma to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":": two young bulls, one ram, and seven male lambs a year old, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"with their grain offering of fine flour mixed with oil, six quarts with each bull, four quarts with the ram, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and two quarts with each of the seven lambs, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and one male goat to make atonement for yourselves. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:28:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Offer them with their drink offerings in addition to the regular burnt offering and its grain offering. Your animals are to be unblemished."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279350321}